description: This common Cooter purrs with a rating of 5, and a multiplier of 8x. It has a total score of 40, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 3 for North, Box for East, Leverage for South, and 1 for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [40 Votes, Common]
